reviewText: Loved this series.  Jax and the gang.  Charlie Hunnan makes the character seem so azlive in this series.  Miss it all.
This was not playable on any of my dvd players. It should have been told that coming from the UK it was different and cannot be played on our players

I'm pretty sure this is the one I bought from but make sure you are in the same country as the seller. I bought a copy from the UK. Can't even watch it because of "regional restrictions." Money wasted
